name: Avocado Prices
data_intro: This data was downloaded from the Hass Avocado Board website in May of 2018 & compiled into a single CSV. Here's how the [Hass Avocado Board describes the data on their website][1]:

cat_feature_intro.region: - `Region` - the city or region of the observation

num_feature_intro.AveragePrice: - `AveragePrice` - the average price of a single avocado
num_feature_intro.Total Volume: - `Total Volume` - Total number of avocados sold
num_feature_intro.4046: - `4046` - Total number of avocados with PLU 4046 sold
num_feature_intro.4225: - `4225` - Total number of avocados with PLU 4225 sold
num_feature_intro.4770: - `4770` - Total number of avocados with PLU 4770 sold
